msgid "ONEZ is a native decentralized, collateral-backed digital asset pegged to USD. It is created by users via borrowing against multiple collateral. When user repays their ONEZ borrow position, the protocol burns that user's ONEZ. All the interest payments accrued by minters of ONEZ would be directly transferred to the ZeroLend treasury."
